@startuml
title Flow F-004: Department governance

actor Caller
participant "Department API" as DepartmentAPI
participant "Department Policy" as DepartmentPolicy
participant "Department Service" as DepartmentService
participant "Audit Service" as AuditService

Caller -> DepartmentAPI: Request governance action
DepartmentAPI -> DepartmentPolicy: Verify role + relationship
DepartmentPolicy --> DepartmentAPI: Decision
DepartmentAPI -> DepartmentService: Execute allowed action
DepartmentService --> DepartmentAPI: Persisted outcome
DepartmentAPI -> AuditService: Persist audit outcome
DepartmentAPI --> Caller: Action response
@enduml
